message: "If you use Suede Creator Skills, please cite it as below."
title: "Suede Creator Skills"
abstract: >-
  A public, open-source (MIT) pack of 21 installable Agent Skills for Claude Code
  and OpenAI Codex, plus an optional Model Context Protocol (MCP) server. Covers
  design, anti-slop copywriting, SEO/AEO/AI EO audits, reference-site restyling
  (Suedify), website visibility and CTA grading, A-F code grading, agent QA,
  launch packaging, artist-campaign tools, and creator rights utilities.
type: software
